# ShebaHack

A platform that connects communities with customers who need large quantities of handmade or local products.

Instead of relying on a single producer, the platform allows groups of community members to collaborate and fulfill bulk orders by distributing the workload among multiple contributors.

## Goal

Support community-based production and make it easier for businesses or individuals to place large orders that local communities can fulfill together.

## Project Structure

* **frontend/** – User interface for customers and community members
* **backend/** – Server logic, APIs, and order management

## Team

ShebaHack Hackathon Team
